goal: Tunu i tētahi kākahu Cranberry/āporo hararei i te kāinga.
sol1: Peel and core 2 large or 3 medium apples (tart ones are best), Horoia e 2 kapu cranberries hou tāpiri ki te āporo.  Tapahia te āporo kia angiangi te āporo, tauhiuhia ki te 1/4 kapu Wai Rēmana.  Whakamahia te Pillsbury Cinnamon roll (momo ngongo) mai i te wāhanga whakamātao i te mākete, me te pine takahuri, takahuri kia iti iho i te 1/2 inihi te mātotoru.  Whakarārangitia te pūtake o tētahi parai tunu konganuku hōhonu ki te paraoa pokepoke.  Rāhuitia te 1/3 o te paraoa pokepoke hei taupoki.  (Ka whakatakotoria tēnei ki runga i muri i tō whakaoti i te whakarite i te whakakī.)  Purua ngā āporo me ngā cranberries ki roto i te rihi ki runga i te paraoa pokepoke.  Tauhiuhia kia 1 kapu huka granulated, 2 tbs. Huka parauri 2 punetēpu hinamona, 1/2 kapu pata (I roto i ngā wāhanga iti), ki runga.  Tauhiuhia te 1/2 pauna tote ki runga.  Purua he kirinuku ki runga i ngā mea katoa.  Tunu ki roto i te oumu i te 375 mō te 40 meneti.  Tangohia mai i te oumu ina parauri te kirinuku me te porohita.  Kia ngahau.
